<h2>Theme!</h2>
<p>How I My Future Friends is about a first year student, starting his new degree in Groningen. Here, the student will have the time of his life and go on many adventures. However, the student will start a new education in a new city where he doesn't know anyone yet. Fortunately the study association is organizing the introductory camp where the new student will meet all his peers. The camp, themed 'TV-series', will be the start of a new stage in the life of the student...</p>